post_cb({"27488862": {"CommentCount": "2", "AcceptedAnswerId": "27489302", "PostTypeId": "1", "LastEditorUserId": "3561240", "CreationDate": "2014-12-15T16:42:52.057", "LastActivityDate": "2015-10-25T16:34:09.947", "LastEditDate": "2014-12-15T16:47:55.613", "ViewCount": "250", "FavoriteCount": "1", "Title": "How do I create a noexcept function pointer?", "Id": "27488862", "Score": "9", "Body": "<p>I'd like to create a function pointer like this:</p>\n<pre><code>void(*function_pointer)()noexcept;\n</code></pre>\n<p>But, this doesn't work. It seems that an exception specifier in a function declaration is invalid. There must be a way to do this though. <em>Right?</em></p>\n<p><em>This was linked to a question that is not the same as this. Here I'm asking how to create a function pointer with a noexcept specifier. That was not asked or answered in the question \"noexcept specifiers in function typedefs\".</em></p>\n", "Tags": "<c++><c++11><function-pointers><noexcept>", "OwnerUserId": "3561240", "AnswerCount": "1"}, "27489302": {"ParentId": "27488862", "PostTypeId": "2", "CommentCount": "0", "Body": "<p>[except.spec]/2:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p id=\"so_27488862_27489302_0\"><strong>An <em>exception-specification</em> shall appear only on a</strong> function declarator\n  for a function type, <strong>pointer to function type</strong>, reference to function\n  type, or pointer to member function type that is the top-level type of\n  a declaration or definition, or on such a type appearing as a\n  parameter or return type in a function declarator.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>So your declaration is indeed well-formed, and Clang <a href=\"http://coliru.stacked-crooked.com/a/631dc711859b1a4d\" rel=\"nofollow\">compiles it</a>.</p>\n<p>Presumably your compiler is not up to date.</p>\n", "OwnerUserId": "3647361", "LastEditorUserId": "3647361", "LastEditDate": "2015-10-25T16:34:09.947", "Id": "27489302", "Score": "7", "CreationDate": "2014-12-15T17:08:31.700", "LastActivityDate": "2015-10-25T16:34:09.947"}, "bq_ids": {"n4140": {"so_27488862_27489302_0": {"section_id": 3364, "quality": 1.0, "length": 28}}, "n3337": {"so_27488862_27489302_0": {"section_id": 3234, "quality": 1.0, "length": 28}}, "n4659": {"so_27488862_27489302_0": {"section_id": 8605, "quality": 0.5714285714285714, "length": 16}}}});